snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you to Coke studio India for creating such a masterpiece 🎉❤.
Uttarakhand is the land of wonders and mesmerizing beauty.....a land full of spiritual and divine energy....also known as devbhoomi 🙏🙏
    You have beautifully portrayed the pahadi elements like the costume ( nath, maangtika, pichora, paunchi, galoband ), Hudka ( a musical instrument) and the aipan art on stairs. From the song to the video, everything is so beautiful 😍❤️

Cut to this day entire Uttarakhand is shining on Coke studio feels nothing less than a dream . 
Thank you coke studio from the bottom of my heart❤❤❤❤❤
